pageTitle: Prime Minister’s itinerary for Monday, January 30, 2023 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

National Capital Region, Canada

Private meetings 

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

6:30 p.m. The Prime Minister will deliver remarks at a Tamil Heritage Month Reception hosted by the Member of Parliament for Scarborough—Rouge Park, Gary Anandasangaree and the Minister of National Defence, Anita Anand.

Note for media:

  • Pooled coverage
